&lt;p&gt;Trusted by companies that are one or one hundred years old, Endor Labs secures code whether it was written by humans or AI, and whether it&#39;s 40-year old C++ code or cutting edge Bazel Monorepos. Endor Labs was founded by serial entrepreneurs Varun Badhwar and Dimitri Stiliadis, and is backed by leading VC firms such as Dell Technology Capital, Lightspeed, and Sierra Ventures.&lt;/p&gt;
