&lt;p data-start=&quot;703&quot; data-end=&quot;1274&quot;&gt;AI is not an add-on at Endor—it’s the core execution fabric of the platform. You’ll be responsible for productizing agentic capabilities that make security teams meaningfully faster and more accurate, translating real AppSec use cases (auto-triage, reachable-only findings, secure design review, PR feedback, remediation suggestions) into reliable agent workflows with clear inputs, outputs, SLAs, and success criteria. This role goes beyond writing requirements and focuses on delivering intuitive, enterprise-grade, AI-first product experiences for modern AppSec teams.&lt;/p&gt;
